  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Class: APPOINTMENT OFFER - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
A record of the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_appointment_date_offered">APPOINTMENT DATE OFFERED</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_appointment_time_offered">APPOINTMENT TIME OFFERED</xref>
 for an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment">APPOINTMENT</xref>
 to a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 and the date and time that the offer or request was made.        </p>
    <p>
More than one 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment_offer">APPOINTMENT OFFER</xref>
 can be made to a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 for an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment">APPOINTMENT</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
When a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 accepts an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment_offer">APPOINTMENT OFFER</xref>, the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_appointment_date_offered">APPOINTMENT DATE OFFERED</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_appointment_time_offered">APPOINTMENT TIME OFFERED</xref>
 of the offer becomes the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_appointment_date">APPOINTMENT DATE</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_appointment_time">APPOINTMENT TIME</xref>
 of the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment">APPOINTMENT</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
Where more than one 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment_offer">APPOINTMENT OFFER</xref>
 has been made for an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment">APPOINTMENT</xref>
 and one has been accepted all the other offers for the same 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment">APPOINTMENT</xref>
 should be marked as refused.        </p>
